verry funny their research threatened when they fail to nab a grant , two fertility doctors , alex hesse ( arnold schwarzenneger ) and larry arbogast ( danny devito ) , test their theory and implant hesse with an embryo . they 'd initially planned to terminate the pregnancy after the first 3 months , but mr. mom-to-be soon decides to go the whole 9 months ... morning sickness , stretch marks and all . plus , hesse is smitten with a fellow scientist ( emma thompson )